íŸ@73e7290eba315d5197285e81cec68e0d20bbee9e39f0105fea75ea18dea55d03⁄Title: title: math stddev
Path: Examples
Content:
Compute the standard deviation of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1 2 3 4 5] | math stddev
1.4142135623730951

```
Compute the sample standard deviation of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1 2 3 4 5] | math stddev --sample
1.5811388300841898

```
Compute the standard deviation of each column in a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | math stddev
‚ï≠‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïÆ
